parameters.name: SC_X
parameters.description: Column contains spacecraft jovicentric (Jupiter fixed) X position in units of jovian radii.

parameters.name: SC_Y
parameters.description: Column contains spacecraft jovicentric (Jupiter fixed) Y position in units of jovian radii.

parameters.name: SC_Z
parameters.description: Column contains spacecraft jovicentric (Jupiter fixed) Z position in units of jovian radii.

parameters.name: VEL_X
parameters.description: Column contains spacecraft velocity jovicentric X component in units of kilometers/second.

parameters.name: VEL_Y
parameters.description: Column contains spacecraft velocity jovicentric Y component in units of kilometers/second.

parameters.name: VEL_Z
parameters.description: Column contains spacecraft velocity jovicentric Z component in units of kilometers/second.

parameters.name: SC_R
parameters.description: Column contains Jupiter to spacecraft range in units of jovian radii.

parameters.name: SC_LAT
parameters.description: Column contains spacecraft jovicentric latitude (positive northward) in degrees.

parameters.name: SC_LON
parameters.description: Column contains spacecraft jovicentric east (system III) longitude in degrees.

parameters.name: CARTSYS3_TO_SPHSYS3
parameters.description: This 3x3 array contains the 9 1pe15.8 rotation matrix elements for converting from Cartesian System III to Spherical System III coordinates.

parameters.name: SC_TO_CARTSYS3
parameters.description: This 3x3 array contains the 9 1pe15.8 rotation matrix elements for converting from Payload (Spacecraft) to Cartesian System III coordinates.

parameters.name: SC_TO_SPHSYS3
parameters.description: This 3x3 array contains the 9 1pe15.8 rotation matrix elements for converting from Payload (Spacecraft) to Spherical System III coordinates.
